            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Breve de supradicta terra de Franciano. In nomine Domini, amen. <persName
                            key="#Count" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/97"
                            >Rainerius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs>, filius quondam <persName key="#Count"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/102">Ildibrandi</persName> item <rs
                            key="#Count">comes</rs>, reflutavit ad <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                        et <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs> Dei et <orgName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/juridical_persons/78"
                            key="#Churches #Monasteries">Sancti Quilici</orgName> de loco <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/86">Populonii</placeName>, idest
                        medietatem de <geogName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/85"
                            key="#Curtes"><rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs>
                            <placeName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/89"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Franciani</placeName></geogName> et de omnibus ad supradictam
                        curtem pertinentibus, vel que ei pertinere videntur, idest nominative, <rs
                            key="#Saltworks">salinis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay">pascuis, pratis</rs>,
                        saltibus, cultis vel incultis, laboratoriis vel non laboratoriis cum aquis
                        aquarumque decursibus, et [..] dedit investituram iam supradictus comes ad
                        proprietatem in manus <persName key="#Monks">Peregrini</persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monachi</rs> de ipso monasterio, ut poneret eam super
                        sanctum <rs key="#Altars">altare</rs> ipsius monasterii; quod et factum est.
                        Supradictus comes fecit istam investitionem in loco ubi dicitur
                            <placeName>Monte Scalochio</placeName>, in presentia <persName
                            key="#Viscount" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/105"
                            >Teudici</persName>
                        <rs key="#Viscount">vicecomitis</rs> sui et <persName>Bernardi</persName>
                        quondam <persName>Teudici</persName> et <persName>Ezulo</persName> da
                            <placeName>Conio</placeName> et <persName>Wilielmo</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Ugi</persName> et aliorum quamquam plurimi qui ibi aderant ad
                        firmitates suas. Anno ab incarnatione Domini millesimo nonagesimo quarto,
                        septimo kalendas septembris. </ab>
